title: Headshot Lugia - Old Perfomance
body:
I found a video in my documents and  dont remember doing it, 
but i remember the the plays i made - they were quite good. :)

It was during the time, azir was so popular. :D

**Why i called the video old performance?**

At this time, i was pretty high in "hidden elo" Normals - 
Most of the time i played with ranked restricted Diamond people, but sometimes even master/challenger showed up in my game.

The games were pretty intense most of time, cause everyone had a good skill and it was really challenging, some would say

the hell in elo heaven. :D

have fun with the video  

**Headshot Lugia**
